PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772041213
OL,3,CUK-first study targets 'dangerous'
OL,4,Coveruse of asthma inhalers in children
OL,6,FThe Prescription Alerts for Reliever
OL,7,FInhalers in Children (PARC) study, led
OL,8,Fby University Hospital Southampton
OL,9,F(UHS), is the first of its kind to
OL,10,Fformally investigate whether proactive
OL,11,Fcheck-ups can prevent life-threatening
OL,12,Fasthma attacks.
OL,14,FFor seven-year-old Amelia, severe
OL,15,Fasthma was once a barrier to a normal
OL,16,Fchildhood.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772041213
OL,3,CUK-first study targets 'dangerous'
OL,4,Coveruse of asthma inhalers in children
OL,6,F"It kind of stopped me from running
OL,7,Faround with my friends," Amelia says.
OL,8,FHer mother, Atlanta McDermott,
OL,9,Fdescribes her daughter as a "really
OL,10,Factive little girl" who loves dance,
OL,11,Fbasketball, and dodgeball, but noted
OL,12,Fhow the condition took its toll.
OL,14,F"It affects daily activities.
OL,15,FSometimes she doesn't want to do them
OL,16,Fbecause she's so tired from having a
OL,17,Fwheeze or being up all night."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772041213
OL,3,CUK-first study targets 'dangerous'
OL,4,Coveruse of asthma inhalers in children
OL,6,FBefore joining the study in December,
OL,7,FAmelia was using her blue "reliever"
OL,8,Finhaler every single day. Since being
OL,9,Finvited for an enhanced check-up and
OL,10,Freceiving new treatment and education,
OL,11,Fthe family has seen a dramatic change.
OL,13,F"She's getting a lot more sleep, and
OL,14,Fshe's just so much more happier," says
OL,15,FAtlanta. "Amelia doesn't use her blue
OL,16,Finhaler anymore. Instead, she takes
OL,17,Fher powdered combination inhaler...
OL,18,Fand that keeps her symptoms under
OL,19,Fcontrol."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772041213
OL,3,CUK-first study targets 'dangerous'
OL,4,Coveruse of asthma inhalers in children
OL,6,FWhile blue inhalers are effective at
OL,7,Falleviating immediate symptoms, they
OL,8,Fdo not treat the underlying airway
OL,9,Finflammation.
OL,11,FExperts warn that overusing them can
OL,12,Fmask serious underlying causes.
OL,13,FResearch highlights a stark risk:
OL,14,Fchildren prescribed six or more
OL,15,Freliever inhalers in a year are 3-5
OL,16,Ftimes more likely to suffer a severe
OL,17,Fasthma attack than those prescribed
OL,18,Fnone.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
