PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772041213
OL,3,CUK-first study targets 'dangerous'
OL,4,Coveruse of asthma inhalers in children
OL,6,FDr. Anna Selby, lead researcher and
OL,7,FPaediatric Registrar at UHS, explains
OL,8,Fthe goal of the PARC study:
OL,10,FWith more than 7 million people
OL,11,Faffected by asthma in the UK and
OL,12,Fapproximately 1,400 deaths annually,
OL,13,Fgetting treatment right is paramount.
OL,15,FThe study is currently recruiting
OL,16,Ffamilies across Hampshire, Dorset, and
OL,17,Fthe Thames Valley. Participating GP
OL,18,Fpractices are split into two groups:
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
